invalid type: string "•Query Transformation: HyDE, query decomposition, step-back prompting \n•Re-ranking & Fusion: Multi-retriever fusion + Cohere/bge reranker \n•Post-retrieval: Contextual compression, chunk fusion \n•Agentic layer (optional stretch): Tool use (e.g., query Jira API for live ticket status) \n•Guardrails: LlamaGuard / NeMo Guardrails – block PII leaks, harmful content"